name: Holly Hobbie Fabric picture
description:
This gorgeous Holly Hobbie inspired picture will take you back to swap cards and patchwork pinafores!

Holly Hobbie is made from 3 different fabrics, and sits on a pink and white sear-sucker background, complete with satin ribbon to hold her bonnet on and little denim boots.

Dimensions:

Picture - 121mm x 170mm
Frame - 192mm x 240mm

White wooden frame has hinged stand, or can be mounted on wall.

name: Wendy Bird
description:
Hanging 'Wendy bird' ornament with contrasting fabric on each side.  

The side pictured is aqua blue with strawberries, other side is white with pink and blue flowers.

Wing made from recycled denim, with button eyes and felt beak, 
satin two tone ribbon and bell detail.

Looks lovely as a room decoration hanging on a door or cupboard handle.  Raw edges designed to fray to add character.

Bird is approx 16cm wide, ribbon hangs approx 23cm.

If you would like to see the fabric on reverse side please contact me and I will send additional photos.
